data.description: (Attention buyers: Loan is assumable for qualified buyers! 3.125% That's a significant monthly payment savings!!!!!) Beautiful waterfront lake home on a corner lot. Extensive 2 story addition added to the home recently along with an oversized covered deck. 3 bedrooms on the second level with vaulted ceilings and a large bathroom. Primary suite has a built in bookcase....or is it? Move it forward to discover a secret doorway to your closet.  The main level is spacious and open. The layout can be designed to fit your lifestyle and needs. Kitchen is creative with butcher block countertops and open space.  Full bathroom on the main level for added convenience. Extra large basement including a new addition under the 2 story section. It's a must see in person! Schedule your showing today!
